    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42424</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_073_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>きみたち、ぼくがいない間、
大丈夫だった？　泣いてない？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>While I was away...were you kids ok? You've not been crying, have you?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42524</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_073_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>泣いてないって。
オレらは赤ん坊じゃないんだぞ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Nah, haven't cried a tiny bit. I'm not a baby anymore, you know?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42664</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_073_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そうだよ、ちょっと心細かったけど、
&lt;Rody&gt;さんや&lt;Suzu&gt;ちゃんのおかげで平気だったよ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We've been fine. It was a bit lonely but thanks to &lt;Rody&gt; and &lt;Suzu&gt; everything was just fine.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42768</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_073_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>なんのなんの。
&lt;Mel&gt;ちゃんはちょっと涙目だったけど</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh, really? From where I'm looking from you seemed to be holding a river of tears all this time.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42876</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_073_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あれは眠くてアクビしたからですっ！
な、泣いてないもん！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>T-those were just yawn tears because I was so tired! I'm telling you, I didn't cry!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43000</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_073_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そっか……ぼくがいなかったせいで
夜も眠れない寂しい想いしたんだね……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's right... You poor thing must have been drowning in worries because I wasn't there. It's all my fault you couldn't get proper sleep.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43080</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_073_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あ……そ、そうじゃなくて……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>N-not at all!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43152</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_073_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>相変わらずの心配性</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>As always worrying for all of us, huh?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
